{
  "stem": "748.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By truck.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, they [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], right and left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I got the idea what this meant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] we was on the [NON-ENGLISH], number 25.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how we survived the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, they give us-- you know, I was young-- I don't know, 18 or 19 year old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took-- give me off a block the change.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There, Yoli.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I met Yoli and Ilka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody thought that we are sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they take me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't sleep now in a cabin together with the fluechtlinge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fluechtlinge, this is, in German, the people what they are under arrest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she says-- she came and took us, a couple girls what we was the special one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we was young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, she took us in her block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to me, she says, you come with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she took me in in a little room what's very nice, clean, nice bed, the nice bedding.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we was, like everybody know in Auschwitz, this is the three sisters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and then, she told me, once, they make our registration, and she tell me, Sasha, you say that you are a mischling.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A mischling?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The father is Catholic, and the mother was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I give it this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And thanks to this, what she teach me, I survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did-- I-- Because of that, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took we once in crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was already a couple minute-- a couple second, I saw the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], the water that came, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started to feel already scratching in the throat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was 3,000 women this time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw so many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody naked.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
